Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:13.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sanada and Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:22.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cheer her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:43.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:51.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Or whether it was... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:56.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I were to be allowed to have a wish come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:02.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd wish it was love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hope it was love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:15.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really would.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:28.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:37.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:40.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:52.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi? That rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:56.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:08.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:12.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:19.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi should be thankful of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:24.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she trying to screw me over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:25.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:32.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tell me, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:36.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my guess, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:40.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how I'm pretty sharp, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:45.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always had a feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:51.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she likes Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:04:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm like Ryu's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi huh? Kurumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of lame, her getting jealous of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:13.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's obvious she's liked Kazehaya the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you never noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:04:59.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:09.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:30.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.76,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Like!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:06:00.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:06.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I just like Kazehaya-kun that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:31.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't have romantic feelings for Sanada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nice, and he helped me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:41.32,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:50.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:52.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:21.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something horribly rude about Sanada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but, as a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admire him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:37.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:43.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this what it means to like someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling I have towards Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:08:00.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanted to be the one helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a hypocrite, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:23.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be able to cheer for you all the time from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not who you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:36.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:51.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Selfish or self-centered, do anything for me or don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:53.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what do you think about going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:08.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going out where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean, as boyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so grown-up, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:23.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even begin to imagine it; it's totally alien to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:30.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably never even imagined going out with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:17.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait, if she likes Kazehaya, then why would she help out someone who likes him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:22.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, she doesn't want him to have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:27.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole point was to make that stupid pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:31.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she set up all those decoys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't have to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu, Sadako was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I met her already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Called you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:58.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think this is from her, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This obviously isn't Sadako's writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find that in your shoebox?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:10.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone come when you were with Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:21.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta and um... that long-haired girl with the summer-ish sounding name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that evil grin, Yano-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:32.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:37.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, but let's go to Kurumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you stopping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Yano-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know things that I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:50.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was keeping quiet until I was confident because I knew you'd run off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:54.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go then, you have confidence now right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need more evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evidence that Kurumi could never dismiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:11.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll pound her into a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:29.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you coming back, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have gone after him and interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But that would have annoyed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:39.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't go out with her, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, come back, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:44.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:46.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:51.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:56.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just cleaning this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and do it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:10.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another member has the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the keys, hurry up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:35.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:39.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go already? Kazehaya's going to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she squirming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she everywhere I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she leading me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:55.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm not into kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have fallen for me if I was a woman too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:10.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to put it this way, you're 10 years early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:10.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:14.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:16.46,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to get rejected here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,By {\i1}him{\i0} of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:21.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Settle for some brat from your own class or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:31.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't mean to eavesdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:39.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta, you damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're slacking, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:44.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:49.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect. I'll find you some really hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:04.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go telling people, Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who asked for your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:24.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like, by the time we knew, everyone was talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:29.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't know if it was her that started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:33.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I can't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:37.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one really remembers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should hit up division A.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:41.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:45.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tomo and Ekkou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:47.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's try asking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:55.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I saw her making rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi? For sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's with Kazehaya sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:03.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:04.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:05.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:10.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time I heard rumors about Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:14.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember being surprised at how bad the rumor's gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:17.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Tomo, Ekkou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:19.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, Yano-chin, now—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:25.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you, Kurumi, you bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! Yano-chin's evil-stepmother-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Tomo, Ekkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:37.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, I'll even make you fess up what brand of toner you use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that sort of personal? Yano-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.35,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe they're at volleyball practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:01.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“There's someone I like.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:06.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they'd say if I told them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:14.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:15.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadowboxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The twist?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:32.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even better than I thought, being in a world not all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,To like Kazehaya-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:45.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and to be able to tell people about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,is such a happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:52.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:15.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan told me her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell her mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:24.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized, we can talk about love together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:32.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, what's this about, Kurumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:38.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you never spread any rumors, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the girls from division A backing me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it's like a samurai drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:59.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did spread that rumor, that's not proof that I started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:05.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this succulent, spotless face of yours still going to talk smack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:12.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I can't tell the difference between maintained skin and unmaintained skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin, you're getting personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:20.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We asked everyone in the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.67,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi's being different too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Chizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:34.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Kurumizawa Ume, we checked your handwriting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and here's the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this is your writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liars go to hell, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Chizu, you did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem pretty different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:08.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, about that, did it work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:09.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:23.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan, Chizu-chan, Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:31.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you three together much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:33.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we were hanging her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:39.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanging?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:43.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rumor from inside the washroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:44.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:06.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, it was Kurumi that made you suffer so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:30.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer that I found and want to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Kurumi
